Happy Earth Day! 🌎

At ICAT Logistics, we believe in giving back to the planet where we can! We do this through various efforts, including but not limited to:

♻️ Reducing our use of paper through EDI capabilities to transmit and receive shipment documentation, as well as utilizing ACH and paperless invoices for our customers;
♻️ Participating in the SmartWay Program to reduce our carbon footprint through the use of more environmentally conscious carriers;
♻️ Focusing on supply chain sustainability by measuring, benchmarking, and improving freight transportation efficiency;
♻️ Educating our team members on the importance of reusing and repurposing materials; and 
♻️ Working with charities who care about corporate responsibility and helping their communities

We will continue to do our part to give back to the environment and our community. If you want to learn more about the SmartWay Program, click here: https://lnkd.in/gxEsQUm

How do you plan on giving back to the planet?

